cat << EOF
Laptop Mode Tools is a laptop power-saving package for Linux systems.
It allows you to extend the battery life of your laptop, in several ways. It is
the primary way to enable the Laptop Mode feature of the Linux kernel, which
lets your hard drive spin down. In addition, it allows you to tweak a number of
other power-related settings using a simple configuration file.
EOF
